examples.en: My piano needs to be tuned.
The project is still under discussion, so stay tuned.
The place tuned me to a solemn mood.

These instruments are very finely tuned.
The radio was tuned to a classical station.
The copilot tuned the radio to hear the message.
He keeps his engine tuned for optimal performance.
All his life was religiously tuned.
